THE CODE USED IN THIS EXERCISE

dplyr         : package for tid data
getwd()       : to get the current directory location
setwd()       : to set directory where to work
read.table()  : to read txt document file
rbind()       : to bind the row to merge 2 data sets
cbind()       : to bind the columns to merge 2 data sets
select()      : to select specific columns from a data set
names()       : to set the column names
gsub()        : to change the column name
write.table() : to get the final output txt file
